dct_description_sm: Concerns war between Poland and Ukraine over boundary disputes following dissolution of Austria-Hungary.
Color legend (French and English) shows lines proposed by "the Armistice Commission," "the Ukrainians," and "the Poles for the establishment of a common front with the Rumanian Forces."
